      "Found 13 feature pairs with correlation > 0.8\n",
      "  - Temp_Avg_C & Temp_Max_C: 0.945\n",
      "  - Temp_Avg_C & Temp_Min_C: 0.946\n",
      "  - Temp_Max_C & Temp_Min_C: 0.930\n",
